      "text": "享受 这孤独 就想歇歇脚",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 194.71,
      "time_str": "03:14.710",
      "text": "这样也挺好 依偎在死角",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 201.04,
      "time_str": "03:21.040",
      "text": "别回眸 相信我 很快就会好",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 204.11,
      "time_str": "03:24.110",
      "text": "活着 或者活着",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 205.04,
      "time_str": "03:25.040",
      "text": "只是为了活着 何以为乐",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 207.04,
      "time_str": "03:27.040",
      "text": "被放了鸽子自我救赎的肖申克",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 209.39,
      "time_str": "03:29.390",
      "text": "又何止一个",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 210.71,
      "time_str": "03:30.710",
      "text": "患得患失面对舍得选择什么",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 213.19,
      "time_str": "03:33.190",
      "text": "你也无可奈何",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 214.46,
      "time_str": "03:34.460",
      "text": "猎豹不再奔跑换取门票",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 217.06,
      "time_str": "03:37.060",
      "text": "这样的囚鸟 又何止一个",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 218.46,
      "time_str": "03:38.460",
      "text": "是否信仰理想",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 220.27,
      "time_str": "03:40.270",
      "text": "可以预算出她的价值观她的市值",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 222.36,
      "time_str": "03:42.360",
      "text": "是否天才和疯子",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 224.07,
      "time_str": "03:44.070",
      "text": "一左一右是谁掰断了戒尺",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 225.97,
      "time_str": "03:45.970",
      "text": "天使和恶魔",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 227.26,
      "time_str": "03:47.260",
      "text": "是不是一生都在对峙的双子",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 229.52,
      "time_str": "03:49.520",
      "text": "原告和被告的倒置",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 231.1,
      "time_str": "03:51.100",
      "text": "珍藏被贴上了泯灭的告示",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 232.97,
      "time_str": "03:52.970",
      "text": "到底为了坚持在静止",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 234.37,
      "time_str": "03:54.370",
      "text": "还是静止为了矜持",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 235.94,
      "time_str": "03:55.940",
      "text": "这不知不觉的不知廉耻",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 237.83,
      "time_str": "03:57.830",
      "text": "活着好像走肉行尸",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 239.15,
      "time_str": "03:59.150",
      "text": "坚持理想的立场的梦想",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 240.73,
      "time_str": "04:00.730",
      "text": "不加掩饰下现实的限制",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 242.93,
      "time_str": "04:02.930",
      "text": "是否真的有着先知",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 244.31,
      "time_str": "04:04.310",
      "text": "告诉我这事情的事实",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 245.99,
      "time_str": "04:05.990",
      "text": "好让我立誓对这信仰开始了加持",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 248.29,
      "time_str": "04:08.290",
      "text": "你怕不怕死",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 250.19,
      "time_str": "04:10.190",
      "text": "如果死亡换来了飞翔",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 251.82,
      "time_str": "04:11.820",
      "text": "又未尝不值得一试",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 253.11,
      "time_str": "04:13.110",
      "text": "就让我死于这",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 254.02,
      "time_str": "04:14.020",
      "text": "最真实麦克风前面的一世",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 255.47,
      "time_str": "04:15.470",
      "text": "那就走吧",
      "translation": null
    },
